sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant AGW as Agentgateway Proxy
    participant Secret as K8s Secret (opaque token)
    participant API as Upstream API

    Client->>AGW: Request + Authorization: Bearer user-JWT
    AGW->>AGW: Validate JWT (jwtAuthentication)
    AGW->>Secret: Read secretRef / inline key
    Secret-->>AGW: Static opaque token
    AGW->>API: Request + Authorization: Bearer opaque-token
    API-->>AGW: Response
    AGW-->>Client: Response
    Note over AGW,Secret: Configured via AgentgatewayBackend:<br/>policies.auth.secretRef or policies.auth.key
